  <summary date="2017-04-03T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">White House Accountability for Language Diversity Act

This bill requires the White House and each federal agency to establish and maintain a Spanish, Chinese, Tagalog, and Vietnamese language version of its official website. Any such website may only include official content and may not include links to other Spanish, Chinese, Tagalog, or Vietnamese websites that are not official content.</summary>
